description.displayText: Milagros is very professional. She is bilingual, organized, punctual, and communicative. She texted me regarding her arrival at our house before coming up, which I find considerate when there's a newborn sleeping. We interviewed Milagros for a regular nanny-type position, and though we ultimately went with someone else who had a more flexible schedule, I would not hesitate to hire Milagros for occasional babysitting needs.
